Awe inspiring example of Buddhist religion
Great panoramic views from this sacred site of the sea and surrounding area. Many instagram photos in the courtyard around the Lady Buddha and pagodas. Unique fauna and flora combined with numerous Chinese and Vietnamese statues. Spend two hours and you won‚Äôt regret.
