Beautiful statues
We loved walking around and seeing all of the beautiful statues. Lady Buddha is about 67 meters tall and we could see her from Hoi An. We did see a few monkeys running around which was cool. It's too bad people litter so much.
Written July 8, 2023
MartyPN
245 contributions
Da Nang highlight
The well manicured site containing a range of interesting gardens in conjunction with the Buddhist religious temples and the Lady Buddha statue. Even if you are not religious the site has much to offer in terms of architecture and garden design. The site was meticulously maintained when we visited. There are areas where there is informative material that will enable a degree of understanding of Buddhist culture. You need to have at least an hour to fully appreciate what the site has to offer. If you go to Da Nang and do not visit the Lady Buddha you have missed the best part.
Visited July 2023
