Viewing the Bay
Dec 2023 ‚Ä¢ Couples
Compared to the Macau Lady Buddha this one is miles better. The whole site's grounds are well maintained. Beautiful scenery within the area and viewpoints out onto the bay. There are a lot of vantages with great viewpoints so you'll have a lot of chances to escape crowds here, as this place gets quite crowded. Also note there are large monkeys so if you're in a secluded area be mindful of your surroundings.
