Beautiful Statue and Temple Grounds
Mar 2020 ‚Ä¢ Family
Below the lady buddha on road, there's a money sanctuary on the left. Monkeys come and go, but fence is to keep humans out. Cutie younger monkeys might approach you and be aware of their over productive mothers. Also, it is good to avoid eye contact with monkeys as they are it as signs of agression. When arriving at temple ground was amazed at the size of statue and temple grounds. Bonzai trees adorn the area. It was very beautiful.
